            <show chara="ironRedClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Ironface">……剧团长，您失态了。</speak>
            <show chara="biankaBiteClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">喂！</speak>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">你倒底在故弄玄虚些什么啊，红色的矮子？！</speak>
            <show chara="biankaBiteClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="shakesDisgustedClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Shakespeare">啧。骂人可不好哦，小妹妹。</speak>
            <show chara="shakesConfidentClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Shakespeare">……让我这么说吧。</speak>
            <show chara="shakesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Shakespeare">起初，我完全不知道你所说的“天命”是个怎样的存在。</speak>
